text: L'Aiguillon-la-Presqu'île is a commune. It is in Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in west France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2022 and consists of the former communes of L'Aiguillon-sur-Mer (the seat) and La Faute-sur-Mer. == References == Category:2022 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: L'Aiguillon-la-Presqu'île
